{"tid":464650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人whatsapp搵人咁鐘意嗌人個名先？","createTime":"2017-11-10T17:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T02:51:42.000Z","uid":134002,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"da2fb1c578867ec7fcf180672e42ddeba316004a","tid":464650,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"通常呢種情況都係同唔太熟既朋友傾計先會出現<br />\n<br />\n搵人既時候係都要嗌佢個名 等佢覆你 先肯講你搵佢做乜<br />\n<br />\n佢: Peter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (你都明知我叫peter架喇)<br />\n我:咩事呀<br />\n佢:你聽日有無野做？<br />\n我:無呀<br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以係你嗌名同時講埋你想講既野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果係重要野 我一睇到個msg都會即刻覆你喇"},{"pid":"f2ad93109735548f0c25517134c9a3f3a0fa28ee","tid":464650,"uid":1436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"未見過會嗌名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919929438d2c5c5fbd1e7be7a4da7b80d401b471","tid":464650,"uid":13288,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"現實先會嗌名再講<br />\n啲人whatsapp我都係直接講咩事"},{"pid":"c4ce058e3cc821fde4b7ab17351933b444b7f84b","tid":464650,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f1b284aa198708e33a05196e0d314cffd62dab","tid":464650,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現實先會嗌名再講<br />\n啲人whatsapp我都係直接講咩事</blockquote><br />\n有幾個唔熟既朋友每個搵我都係嗌名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  直接講埋做乜係咪真係咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1109f33ceaf274ec91ec01a3feb055bf2d6bb51b","tid":464650,"uid":132896,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"我以為whatsapp或者其他通訊工具<br />\n都係得<br />\n<br />\n喂<br />\n屌你<br />\n戇鳩仔<br />\n同冇address <br />\n<br />\n呢幾種稱呼方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dad42e2d208730692ca9f732837ada9d52a853","tid":464650,"uid":103823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"我老闆通常會 hi hi 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9453e38dd5ffb476d13955c79a92a6a051b365","tid":464650,"uid":115384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"仲衰嘅係 佢叫完你之後就會深潛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要你等返佢轉頭"},{"pid":"75fc9cd298be12fbb905b0eddef09d8c3e6f70e9","tid":464650,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"閣下，"},{"pid":"91b6811c76ecd672d535130f76b5dc964731bc75","tid":464650,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:08:55.000Z","msg":"你係咪d 無icon無名既人，驚wts錯人姐"},{"pid":"7d530b41d8aea889d9a0b28c4b1a160ccc229975","tid":464650,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"岩呀屌"},{"pid":"91e039a1306e71f05f6ebf6716e15affd841e8ec","tid":464650,"uid":6532,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"禮貌"},{"pid":"467d4a57550e84df49536b748def301493aac963","tid":464650,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:32:02.000Z","msg":"睇下你有無反應"},{"pid":"b2bc153c39612405b810f6bb3a8a700ffbd89533","tid":464650,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:36:11.000Z","msg":"點解要嗌名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接講做乜咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0759cba1fd67e7d8836758b7af84af6a466860f3","tid":464650,"uid":155254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:40:19.000Z","msg":"嗌名先係某方面既標準程序. 有時慣咗好難改. 如以下例子:<br />\n<br />\n例一:<br />\n<br />\n你: Susan         (你都明知佢叫 Susan 架喇)<br />\n佢: 咩事呀<br />\n你: 褂住妳啦 <br />\n佢: 我都係呀<br />\n<br />\n例二:<br />\n<br />\n你: 褂住妳啦<br />\n佢: 我係 Susan 老公. 你係邊撚個?<br />\n<br />\n清楚末?"},{"pid":"a0e52ec463b6ca758a01728cf060e29f7052aee8","tid":464650,"uid":146924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:44:28.000Z","msg":"通常咁嘅情況即係唔係有chat開<br />\n突然搵人問人嘢/搵人幫手 叫人個名一聲係禮貌嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通咩都唔講直接一句得埋嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a69f0eeb0bc92019506f2f6ba6aeabcda04f171","tid":464650,"uid":126736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:47:26.000Z","msg":"細路唔會明"},{"pid":"159b789ae3d86b3c7727442221074a5c042e2053","tid":464650,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老闆通常會 hi hi 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢實情係未暗地裡鬧緊你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0580f3289c509ec5feaa63cbb25e4e181050970","tid":464650,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:18:43.000Z","msg":"我通常會講講，你好，今日天氣幾好，食左飯未呢？做開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d747e4e323e21b087d2e4cd0ad94da00d5354f","tid":464650,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常咁嘅情況即係唔係有chat開<br />\n突然搵人問人嘢/搵人幫手 叫人個名一聲係禮貌嚟嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通咩都唔講直接一句得埋嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係叫名同問野可以一句過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPeter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你聽日得唔得閒呀？"}]}